# 🏗️ System Stack

| Component       | Technology                          |
| --------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Backend         | Python + FastAPI                    |
| Database        | PostgreSQL                          |
| Vector DB       | Qdrant                              |
| Cache           | Redis                               |
| Background Jobs | Arq (default; Celery/Taskiq optional) |
| Object Storage  | S3 / MinIO / Local                  |
| Observability   | Langfuse                            |
| Local LLM       | Ollama                              |
| Production LLM  | vLLM                                |

Background jobs default to **Arq** (Redis-native, async-first, minimal infra). Celery or Taskiq are acceptable alternatives where their feature sets are required, but a deployment should pick exactly one.

