# 🧠 AI Engineering Standards

## Background Processing

Long-running AI tasks must never block HTTP requests.

Examples

* OCR
* Embeddings
* Parsing
* Evaluation

Pattern

```
HTTP Request
      ↓
Redis Queue
      ↓
202 Accepted
      ↓
Worker
```

---

## Hybrid Retrieval

Vector-only search is forbidden. This is the canonical retrieval pipeline.

```
Query
   │
   ├── BM25
   └── Vector Search
            │
            ▼
      Reciprocal Rank Fusion
            │
            ▼
         Reranker
            │
            ▼
     Context Selection
            │
            ▼
            LLM
```

---

## Prompt Management

Never hardcode prompts.

Store prompts in:

* Langfuse
* Database
* Configuration Files

Version every prompt.

---

## Structured Outputs

Prefer:

* JSON Schema
* Pydantic Models
* Tool Calling

Avoid parsing free-form text.

---

